Get the Asset home name

ee_get_assethome()

Value

Character. The name of the Earth Engine Asset home (e.g. users/datacolecfbf)

See also

Other path utils: ee_get_earthengine_path()

Examples

if (FALSE) {
library(rgee)
ee_Initialize()

ee_get_assethome()
}
